</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="520">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Collection of three scientific works, nearly contemporary with the life of the author:  one work on cosmology and astronomy, one on arithmetic, and one on the division of time according to the movements of the sun and moon.  The first work originally followed the second and third, and the beginning of the second work is missing.</marc:subfield>
